com.wizzer.mle.runtime.core

Class MleTables

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.util.Observable
      • com.wizzer.mle.runtime.core.MleTables

  • public class MleTables
extends java.util.Observable
    This class is used to define and register the tables generated for a Magic Lantern application.
    Author:
    Mark S. Millard

      • registerObject

        public void registerObject(IMleObject obj)
        Register the specified Magic Lantern Object.

        Note that this class does not actually manage the registration of the MLE Object. Instead it passes the Object on to any Observers so that they can determine whether to register the Object or not.

        Parameters:
        obj - The MLE Object to register.

      • unregisterObject

        public void unregisterObject(IMleObject obj)
        Unregister the specified Magic Lantern Object.

        Note that this class does not actually manage the registration of the MLE Object. Instead it passes the Object on to any Observers so that they can determine whether to unregister the Object or not.

        Parameters:
        obj - The MLE Object to unregister.
